     function ToggleMobileQuickLinks()
     {
         if(window.innerWidth < 768)
         {
             jQuery('#MobileQuickLinkWrapper').addClass('MQLvisible');
             jQuery('#MobileQuickLinkWrapper #FixedBottomBar').addClass('MQLvisible');
             jQuery('#quickLinkBarBottomGap').addClass('MQLvisible');

         else

     }
 
            function HideAllLinkItem()
            {
                jQuery('#MobileQuickLinkWrapper #quickCalendar').removeClass('MQLvisible');
                jQuery('#MobileQuickLinkWrapper #BottomBarContentWrapper .quickLinkIcon.booknowIcon').removeClass('MQLselected');
                jQuery('#MobileQuickLinkWrapper #BottomBarContentWrapper #BookNowQuickLink .quickLinkLabel').removeClass('MQLselected');
                jQuery('#MobileQuickLinkWrapper #quickMap').removeClass('MQLvisible');
                jQuery('#MobileQuickLinkWrapper #BottomBarContentWrapper .quickLinkIcon.locationIcon').removeClass('MQLselected');

                jQuery('#MobileQuickLinkWrapper #quickContact').removeClass('MQLvisible');

                jQuery('#MobileQuickLinkWrapper #BottomBarContentWrapper #ContactQuickLink .quickLinkLabel').removeClass('MQLselected');
                jQuery('#MobileQuickLinkWrapper #FixedBottomBar').css('bottom','0px');

     function AccubookOpenLinkItem(index)
     {
         if (index == 1) {
             jQuery('#MobileQuickLinkWrapper #quickCalendar').addClass('MQLvisible');
             jQuery('#MobileQuickLinkWrapper #BottomBarContentWrapper .quickLinkIcon.booknowIcon').addClass('MQLselected');
             jQuery('#MobileQuickLinkWrapper #BottomBarContentWrapper #BookNowQuickLink .quickLinkLabel').addClass('MQLselected');
             jQuery('#MobileQuickLinkWrapper #FixedBottomBar').css('bottom','-70px');
         }
         if (index == 2) {
             jQuery('#MobileQuickLinkWrapper #quickMap').addClass('MQLvisible');
             jQuery('#MobileQuickLinkWrapper #BottomBarContentWrapper .quickLinkIcon.locationIcon').addClass('MQLselected');
             jQuery('#MobileQuickLinkWrapper #BottomBarContentWrapper #LocationQuickLink .quickLinkLabel').addClass('MQLselected');
         }
         if (index == 3) {
             jQuery('#MobileQuickLinkWrapper #quickContact').addClass('MQLvisible');
             jQuery('#MobileQuickLinkWrapper #BottomBarContentWrapper .quickLinkIcon.contactIcon').addClass('MQLselected');
             jQuery('#MobileQuickLinkWrapper #BottomBarContentWrapper #ContactQuickLink .quickLinkLabel').addClass('MQLselected');
         }
         linkItemState = index;
     }
 
     function ToggleLinkItem(index)
     {
         if (linkItemState > 0)
         {
             HideAllLinkItem();
 
             if (linkItemState != index && linkItemState > 0) {
                 AccubookOpenLinkItem(index);
             }
             else {
                 linkItemState = 0;
             }
         }
         else
         {
             AccubookOpenLinkItem(index);
         }
     }
 
     function ToggleQuickMapDirection()
     {
         if (jQuery('#MobileQuickLinkWrapper #quickMap .quickMapContentWrapper .directionsTab').hasClass('MQLvisible'))

         }
         else

             jQuery('#MobileQuickLinkWrapper #quickMap .quickMapContentWrapper .directionsTab').addClass('MQLvisible');
         }
     }
 
     function CloseQuickMapDirection()
     {
         jQuery('#MobileQuickLinkWrapper #quickMap .quickMapContentWrapper .directionsTab').removeClass('MQLvisible');
     }

       <script>
        jQuery(document).ready(function(){
 
                   var nowTemp = new Date();
                   var now = new Date(nowTemp.getFullYear(), nowTemp.getMonth(), nowTemp.getDate(), 0, 0, 0, 0);
                     
                   var quickCheckin = jQuery('#checkinDatepicker').datepicker({
                       beforeShowDay: function (date) {
 
                           return date.valueOf() >= now.valueOf();
                       },
                       endDate: '+365d',
                       format: 'dd/mm/yyyy',
                       weekStart: 1,
                       disableTouchKeyboard: true,
                       todayHighlight: false
                     });
 
                   var quickCheckout = jQuery('#checkoutDatepicker').datepicker({
                       beforeShowDay: function (date) {
                           if (!quickCheckin.datepicker("getDate")) {
                               return date.valueOf() >= new Date().valueOf();
                           } else {
                               return date.valueOf() > quickCheckin.datepicker("getDate").valueOf();
                           }
                       },
                       endDate: '+365d',
                       format: 'dd/mm/yyyy',
                       weekStart: 1,
                       disableTouchKeyboard: true,
                       todayHighlight: false
                   });
 
                   quickCheckin.on('changeDate', function (ev) {
                       var fromDate = new Date(ev.date);
                       var toDate = new Date(ev.date);
                       var maxDate = new Date(ev.date);
                             
                       toDate.setDate(toDate.getDate() + 1);
                       maxDate.setDate(maxDate.getDate() + 30);
                       quickCheckout.datepicker("update", toDate);
                       quickCheckout.datepicker("setEndDate", maxDate);
                    
                       var dateStr=( "0" + quickCheckin.datepicker("getDate").getDate()).slice(-2) + "/" + ( "0" + (quickCheckin.datepicker("getDate").getMonth() + 1)).slice(-2) + "/" + quickCheckin.datepicker("getDate").getFullYear();
                       jQuery('#ctl00_MobileQuickLinks_CheckinQuickDate').html(dateStr);
                       document.getElementById("ctl00_MobileQuickLinks_checkinQuickDateValue").value = dateStr;
 
                       SelectCheckout();
                   });
 
                   quickCheckout.on('changeDate', function (ev) {
                       var dateStr=( "0" + quickCheckout.datepicker("getDate").getDate()).slice(-2) + "/" + ( "0" + (quickCheckout.datepicker("getDate").getMonth() + 1)).slice(-2) + "/" + quickCheckout.datepicker("getDate").getFullYear();
                       jQuery('#ctl00_MobileQuickLinks_CheckoutQuickDate').html(dateStr);
                       document.getElementById("ctl00_MobileQuickLinks_checkoutQuickDateValue").value = dateStr;
 
                       //UpdateNbNights();
 
                       jQuery('#ctl00_MobileQuickLinks_Btn_QuickSearch').removeClass('disabled');
                       jQuery('#ctl00_MobileQuickLinks_Btn_QuickSearch').removeAttr('disabled');
                   });
 
                   //function UpdateNbNights()
                   //{
                   //    var nbNights = Math.floor((quickCheckout.datepicker("getDate") - quickCheckin.datepicker("getDate")) / (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24));
                   //    jQuery('#nbNights').html(nbNights.toString());
                     //}
 
                     jQuery('#ctl00_MobileQuickLinks_Btn_QuickSearch').attr('disabled', true);
 
                 });
 
                 function SearchLoading()
                 {
                     jQuery('#ctl00_MobileQuickLinks_Btn_QuickSearch').addClass('disabled');
                     jQuery('#ctl00_MobileQuickLinks_Btn_QuickSearch').attr('disabled', true);
                     jQuery('#ctl00_MobileQuickLinks_Btn_QuickSearch').html('Submitting...');
                     return true;
                 }
 
                 function SelectCheckout()
                 {
                     if(jQuery('#checkinDatepicker').datepicker("getDate"))
                     {
                         jQuery('#MobileQuickLinkWrapper #quickCalendar .dateSearchWrapper .datepickerWrapper').addClass('selectCheckout');
                         jQuery('#MobileQuickLinkWrapper #quickCalendar .dateSearchWrapper .dateSearchHeader #checkinLabel').removeClass('MQLselected');
                         jQuery('#MobileQuickLinkWrapper #quickCalendar .dateSearchWrapper .dateSearchHeader #checkoutLabel').addClass('MQLselected');
                     }
                 }
 
                 function SelectCheckin()
                 {
                     jQuery('#MobileQuickLinkWrapper #quickCalendar .dateSearchWrapper .datepickerWrapper').removeClass('selectCheckout');
                     jQuery('#MobileQuickLinkWrapper #quickCalendar .dateSearchWrapper .dateSearchHeader #checkinLabel').addClass('MQLselected');
                     jQuery('#MobileQuickLinkWrapper #quickCalendar .dateSearchWrapper .dateSearchHeader #checkoutLabel').removeClass('MQLselected');
                 }
       </script>

    <script type="text/javascript">
     var DirectionsMap = {
         // HTML Nodes
         mapContainer: document.getElementById('googlemap'),
         dirContainer: document.getElementById('directions'),
         //fromInput: document.getElementById('from-input'),
         toInput: document.getElementById('to-input'),
         travelModeInput: document.getElementById('travel-mode-input'),
         unitInput: document.getElementById('unit-input'),
 
         // API Objects
         dirService: new google.maps.DirectionsService(),
         dirRenderer: new google.maps.DirectionsRenderer(),
         map: null,
 
         showDirections: function (dirResult, dirStatus) {
             if (dirStatus != google.maps.DirectionsStatus.OK) {
                 //alert('Directions failed: ' + dirStatus);
                 document.getElementById("directions").innerHTML = '<br><br>Directions failed:  ' + dirStatus;
                 return;
             }
 
             // Show directions
             DirectionsMap.dirRenderer.setMap(DirectionsMap.map);
             DirectionsMap.dirRenderer.setPanel(DirectionsMap.dirContainer);
             DirectionsMap.dirRenderer.setDirections(dirResult);
         },
 
         getSelectedTravelMode: function () {
             var value =
                 DirectionsMap.travelModeInput.options[DirectionsMap.travelModeInput.selectedIndex].value;
             if (value == 'driving') {
                 value = google.maps.DirectionsTravelMode.DRIVING;
             } else if (value == 'bicycling') {
                 value = google.maps.DirectionsTravelMode.BICYCLING;
             } else if (value == 'walking') {
                 value = google.maps.DirectionsTravelMode.WALKING;
             } else {
                 document.getElementById("directions").innerHTML = '<br><br>Unsupported travel mode.';
             }
             return value;
         },
 
         getSelectedUnitSystem: function () {
             return DirectionsMap.unitInput.options[DirectionsMap.unitInput.selectedIndex].value == 'metric' ?
                 google.maps.DirectionsUnitSystem.METRIC :
                 google.maps.DirectionsUnitSystem.IMPERIAL;
         },
 
         getDirections: function () {
 
             var currentLocation;
 
             if(!directionMapRendered)
             {
 
                 if (navigator.geolocation) 
                 {
                     navigator.geolocation.getCurrentPosition(showPosition,showError);
                 } 
                 else 
                 {
                     document.getElementById("directions").innerHTML = "<br><br>Geolocation is not supported by this browser.";
                 }
                 
             }
             else
             {
                 return;
             }
             function showPosition(position) {
                 currentLocation = new google.maps.LatLng(position.coords.latitude, position.coords.longitude);
                 var toStr = DirectionsMap.toInput.value;
 
                 var dirRequest = {
                     origin: currentLocation,
                     destination: toStr,
                     travelMode: DirectionsMap.getSelectedTravelMode(),
                     unitSystem: DirectionsMap.getSelectedUnitSystem(),
                     provideRouteAlternatives: true
                 };
                 DirectionsMap.dirService.route(dirRequest, DirectionsMap.showDirections);
                 directionMapRendered = true;
             }
 
             function showError(error) {
                 switch(error.code) {
                     case error.PERMISSION_DENIED:
                         document.getElementById("directions").innerHTML = "<br><br>Request for Geolocation not accepted or not connected via mobile network."
                         break;
                     case error.POSITION_UNAVAILABLE:
                         document.getElementById("directions").innerHTML = "<br><br>Location information is unavailable."
                         break;
                     case error.TIMEOUT:
                         document.getElementById("directions").innerHTML = "<br><br>The request to get user location timed out."
                         break;
                     case error.UNKNOWN_ERROR:
                         document.getElementById("directions").innerHTML = "<br><br>An unknown error occurred."
                         break;
                 }
                 jQuery('#MobileQuickLinkWrapper #quickMap .quickMapContentWrapper .directionsTab .directionSettings').css('display','none');
             }
 
         },
 
         init: function () {
             try{
                 var latlng = new google.maps.LatLng(parseFloat("54.476628"),parseFloat("-8.284515"));
                 var myOptions = { zoom: 13, center: latlng, mapTypeId: google.maps.MapTypeId.ROADMAP };
                 DirectionsMap.map = new google.maps.Map(DirectionsMap.mapContainer, myOptions);
 
                 var marker = new google.maps.Marker({ position: latlng, animation: google.maps.Animation.DROP, map: DirectionsMap.map });
 
                 var hotel_address = "Main Street Bundoran Bundoran Donegal";
 
                 var contentString = '<div class="info_holder">' +
                     '<div class="info_title">' + "Fitzgeralds Hotel Bundoran" + '</div>' +
                     '<div class="info_content">' + hotel_address + '</div>';
 
                 var infowindow = new google.maps.InfoWindow({
                     content: contentString
                 });
 
                 google.maps.event.addListener(DirectionsMap.map, 'click', function () {
                     infowindow.close();
                 });
 
                 google.maps.event.addListener(marker, 'click', function () {
                     infowindow.open(DirectionsMap.map, marker);
                 });
             }
             catch(ex)
             {
                 console.log("Error loading google API: " + ex.toString());
             }
         }
     };
     google.maps.event.addDomListener(window, 'load', DirectionsMap.init);
    </script>

          <h3 class="title-style1">
           Family Owned For Over 50 Years
           <span class="title-block">
           </span>
          </h3>
          <img alt="Fitzgeralds Hotel Bundoran Co Donegal Ireland" height="250" src="/sites/3161/wwwroot/family-owned-hotel-bundoran.jpg" width="500"/>
          <p>
           Fitzgeralds Hotel in Bundoran, Co Donegal, provides superior 3 Star hotel accommodation, overlooking the famous and picturesque Donegal Bay in the North West of Ireland.
           <br/>
           <br/>
           Owned and run by the same family for over 50 years, Fitzgeralds Hotel Donegal enjoys a well earned reputation for providing a warm, friendly and helpful service individually tailored to each guests needs.
           <br/>
          </p>
          <a href="/about-fitzgeralds-hotel-bundoran/">
           <span class="button1">
            More About Us
           </span>
          </a>
         </div>
         <div class="one-third">
          <h3 class="title-style1">
           Ideally Located In Bundoran
           <span class="title-block">
           </span>
          </h3>
          <img alt="Ideally Located In Bundoran" height="250" src="/sites/3161/wwwroot/ideally-located-bundoran.jpg" width="500"/>
          <p>
           Centrally located in the most fashionable area of Bundoran all amenities, shops and attractions are close at hand.
 Each comfortable and spacious guest bedroom has en-suite bathroom facilities and is fully equipped to the highest modern standards  many enjoy spectacular sea views.
           <br/>
           <br/>
           Informal and comfortably furnished guest lounges are a feature, where guests can sit back, relax and enjoy Irish hospitality at its best.
          </p>
          <a href="/see-and-do-donegal-bundoran/activites-around-bundoran-donegal/">

          <img alt="Relax At Fizgeralds Hotel Bundoran Co Donegal Ireland" height="250" src="/sites/3161/wwwroot/hotel-bundoran-fitzgeralds-hotel.jpg" width="500"/>
          <p>
           As no coach tours or functions are serviced, hotel guests can rest assured that there will be no noisy intrusions to their relaxation. An enclosed private car park provides the added assurance of safety for guests vehicles.
           <br/>
           <br/>
           Fitzgeralds Bistro Restaurant has an established reputation for good food, fine wine and excellent service at reasonable prices, closed Mondays and Tuesdays.
